properties.areaDesc: Tampa Bay waters; Waters from Bonita Beach to Englewood FL out 20 to 60 NM; Coastal waters from Bonita Beach to Englewood FL out 20 NM; Charlotte Harbor and Pine Island Sound; Coastal waters from Englewood to Tarpon Springs FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 4 at 3:21AM EST until January 5 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
6 to 9 feet expected.

* WHERE...Tampa Bay waters, Charlotte Harbor and Pine Island
Sound, Coastal waters from Englewood to Tarpon Springs FL out
20 NM, Coastal waters from Bonita Beach to Englewood FL out 20
NM and Waters from Bonita Beach to Englewood FL out 20 to 60
NM.

* WHEN...From 4 PM this afternoon to 4 PM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 4 PM EST SUNDAY
